  <brief_title>EUS-FNA With and Without Suction</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Single Blind Controlled Trial of EUS-FNA With and Without Suction for Adequate Cellblock Sample Procurement of Solid Pancreatic Mass Lesions Using 25G Needle</official_title>
