  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All patients referred to UAB Endoscopy Unit for assessment of pancreatic mass lesions
             that requires FNA.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Age &lt; 19 years

               -  Unable to safely undergo EUS for any reason

               -  Coagulopathy (INR&gt;1.6, Prothrombin Time&gt;18 secs, Thrombocytopenia &lt; 80,000
                  cells/ml)

               -  Unable to consent

               -  Non-English speaking patients
      </textblock>
